      "text": [
        ": قلت له: في كم أقرأ القرآن؟ فقال: اقرءه أخماسا، اقرءه، أسباعا، أما إن عندي مصحفا مجزى أربعة عشر حزءا"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "[4/-] al-Kafi: Muhammad b. Yahya from Muhammad b. al-Husayn from Ali b. al-Nu’man from Ya’qub b. Shuayb from Husayn b. Khalid from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام. He (Husayn) said: I said to him: In how many (days) should I recite the (whole) Qur’an? He (i.e. the Imam) said: Recite it in fifths, recite it in sevenths, as for me then I have a codex divided into fourteen parts"
        ]
      }
